ols that aim to enhance creative performance in individual and collective situations.\n\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://sciendo-parsed-data-feed.s3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/612ea2dd1000020b549d6272/cover-image.jpg\"/><meta name=\"citation_title\" content=\"Technologies for Supporting Creativity in Design: A View of Physical and Virtual Environments with Regard to Cognitive and Social Processes\"/><meta name=\"citation_author\" content=\"Karima Toumi\"/><meta name=\"citation_author\" content=\"Fabien Girandola\"/><meta name=\"citation_author\" content=\"Nathalie Bonnardel\"/><meta name=\"citation_publication_date\" content=\"2021/06/01\"/><meta name=\"citation_journal_title\" content=\"Creativity. Theories \u2013 Research - Applications\"/><meta name=\"citation_volume\" content=\"8\"/><meta name=\"citation_issue\" content=\"1\"/><meta name=\"citation_firstpage\" content=\"189\"/><meta name=\"citation_lastpage\" content=\"212\"/><meta name=\"citation_pdf_url\" content=\"https://www.sciendo.com/pdf/10.2478/ctra-2021-0012\"/><script async=\"\" src=\"https://badge.dimensions.ai/badge.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script><script src=\"https://crossmark-cdn.crossref.org/widget/v2.0/widget.js\"></script><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"//s7.addthis.com/js/300/addthis_widget.js#pubid=ra-6048be7b4c38021f\"></script><script type=\"text/javascript\">var addthis_config = {\n            ui_click: true,\n            ui_disable: true\n        } </script><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mathjax@2/MathJax.js?config=default\"></script><script type=\"text/x-mathjax-config\">if (MathJax.Hub.Browser.isMSIE) {\n              window.onload = function () {MathJax.Hub.Queue([&quot;Typeset&quot;,MathJax.Hub])}\n            }\n            \n            MathJax.Hub.Config({\n              extensions: [&quot;MMLorHTML.js&quot;],\n              jax: [&quot;input/MathML&quot;,&quot;output/CommonHTML&quot;,&quot;output/NativeMML&quot;],\n      