ions</h6></a></div><div class=\"Chapter_book__details__3Pqvo\"><div><dl class=\"inline side-panel-details\"><dt class=\"dt-title\"> Journal Details  </dt><dd><span><dt class=\"no-seperator\"></dt><dd class=\"m-0\"><a style=\"display:block\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0\"><img height=\"45\" src=\"https://mirrors.creativecommons.org/presskit/buttons/88x31/png/by-nc-nd.png\" alt=\"License\"/></a></dd></span><dt>Format</dt><dd>Journal</dd><dt> First Published</dt><dd>16 Apr 2015</dd><dt> Publication timeframe</dt><dd>2 times per year</dd><dt> Languages</dt><dd>English</dd></dd></dl></div></div></div><div class=\"Chapter_chapterBody__3AzIV\"><div class=\"Chapter_chapterBodyTop__1-7Za\"><div class=\"Chapter_chapterBodyInfo__mm8un Article_chapterBodyInfo__2OEaz row\"><div class=\"col-12\"><dt class=\"no-seperator\"></dt><dd class=\"m-0\"><img width=\"16\" height=\"25\" src=\"/Open_Access_logo_PLoS_transparent.svg\" alt=\"access type\"/><span class=\"open-access\"> Open Access</span></dd><h1 class=\"Article_product__title__1MB1B product__title\"><article-title>Technologies for Supporting Creativity in Design: A View of Physical and Virtual Environments with Regard to Cognitive and Social Processes</article-title></h1></div><div class=\"col-md-9 col-12\"><h6 class=\"Article_article__authors__2Dkuc\"><div class=\"Article_author-popup__1C51E\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"fw-500 color-blue d-none d-md-block\" aria-describedby=\"popup-27392\">Karima Toumi<span style=\"color:#000000\">,</span></a><a href=\"#\" class=\"fw-500 color-blue d-md-none\" aria-describedby=\"popup-27393\">Karima Toumi</a></div><div class=\"Article_author-popup__1C51E\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"fw-500 color-blue d-none d-md-block\" aria-describedby=\"popup-27394\">Fabien Girandola<span style=\"color:#000000\">\u00a0<!-- -->and</span></a><a href=\"#\" class=\"fw-500 color-blue d-md-none\" aria-describedby=\"popup-27395\">Fabien Girandola</a></div><div class=\"Article_aut